WEBVTT

00:00:58.872 --> 00:01:02.397
a bar of soap.

00:01:02.397 --> 00:01:03.829
Washing hands with soap,

00:01:03.829 --> 00:01:06.200
a habit we all take for granted,

00:01:06.200 --> 00:01:08.484
can reduce diarrhea by half,

00:01:08.484 --> 00:01:12.140
can reduce respiratory infections by one third.

00:01:12.140 --> 00:01:13.911
Handwashing with soap

00:01:13.911 --> 00:01:15.560
can have an impact

00:01:15.560 --> 00:01:20.587
on reducing flu, trachoma, SARS,

00:01:20.587 --> 00:01:22.977
and most recently in the case of cholera

00:01:22.977 --> 00:01:25.667
and Ebola outbreak,

00:01:25.667 --> 00:01:27.358
one of the key interventions

00:01:27.358 --> 00:01:30.176
is handwashing with soap.